[Dawson County, Georgia, is in the far north of that state; see: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dawson_County,_Georgia.
Polk County is in NW Georgia on the border with Alabama; see: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polk_County,_Georgia.
The Connecticut report contains a fair map of the state showing the location.

The key to controlling urban rabies is to make sure that domestic dogs and cats are routinely vaccinated whether it is compulsory or not. In rural areas, the same applies, but also ensure your horses are vaccinated. They are worth the expense as are pedigree stock. - Mod.MHJ

